                <note rend="inline" type="source">693.94244/239: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peiping</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-06-30T13:00:00+08:00"
                            >June 30, 1937—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received June 30—4:40 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>191. In a despatch dated June 23 Consulate General at Tientsin reports that
                    importation of kerosene and gasoline by smugglers has not appreciably decreased
                    and that American oil companies business continues to suffer. Standard Vacuum
                    Oil Company and Texas Company suggest that customs authorities be requested to
                    establish a preventive office at the Tientsin East Station which would be
                    empowered to seize smuggled cargo or collect regular duty thereon.
                    Notwithstanding Peiping railway authorities have hitherto shown no disposition
                    to cooperate with customs to suppress smuggling, Embassy requests that it be
                    authorized to make informal representations to the Foreign Office at Nanking
                    with a view to establishment of the preventive office as requested by American
                    Oil Company.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
